001 Запс на прийом
  Precondition
    - test site is opened on the home page: https://medikom.ua/

  Steps
    1. Pres on the button "Запис на прийом"
    2. Fill in the form with valid data
      a. fill in the field "name" with valid data
      b. fill in the field "phone" with valid data
    3. Press on the button "Записатися" (submit)

  Expected result
    1. The form is opened
    2. The fields name is filled with valid data
    3. The fields phone is filled with valid data


002 Find a doctor
  Precondition
    - test site is opened on the home page: https://medikom.ua/

  Steps
    1. Press on the button "Лікарі"
    2. Fill in the search field with valid data (for example "Авершин Валерій Іванович")
    3. Press on the find doctor button

  Expected result
    1. The name of the doctor is equal to the name in the search field
    2. The doctor's page is opened

003 Find all doctors in the clinic by department
    Precondition
        - test site is opened on the home page: https://medikom.ua/

    Steps
        1. Press on the button "Лікарі"
        2. Press on the button "Дітям"
        3. Press on the button "вул. Василя Тютюнника, 37/1"
        4. Press on the button "Всі лікарі" in the department "Ультразвукова діагностика - УЗД"

    Expected result
        1. The all doctors in the clinic by department are displayed
        2. The doctor's description is displayed "Лікар УЗД" and "вул. Василя Тютюнника, 37/1"

004 Left comment about doctor
    Precondition
        - test site is opened on the home page: https://medikom.ua/
        - doctor's page is opened

    Steps
        1. Press on the button "Залишити відгук"
        2. Fill in the form with valid data
            a. fill in the field "name" with valid data
            b. fill in the field "phone" with valid data
            c. select star rating
            d. fill in the field "comment" with valid data
            e. choose the checkbox "Я не робот"
        3. Press on the button "Відправити" (submit)

    Expected result
        1. all fields are with correct data
        2. The comment is displayed on the doctor page

005 Find all doctors in the clinic by department

    Precondition
        - test site is opened on the home page: https://medikom.ua/

    Steps
        1. Press on the button "Дітям"
        2. Press on the button "офтальмологія"
        3. Press on the button "Лікарі"

    Expected result
        1. The all doctors in the clinic by department are displayed
            - Качуровський Богдан Анатолійович
            - Марюхніч Надія Володимирівна
            - Якубовський Сергій Валерійович
            - Буяновська Леся Анатоліївна
            - Павленко Дмитро Олександрович